descriptionHtml:
Here's another minimod with just one texture inside.
I think the armor was called Red&White Zhuliya and now I made it Red&Yellow :D. If you like it, get it, otherwise, stick with the original.

Original mod: [url=http://www.loverslab.com/topic/55715-unpb-tv/page-8#entry1556059]Loverslab link[/url]
UUNP version, not necessary, but strongly recommended: [url=http://wtfuun.tumblr.com/post/144588111526/rw-zhuliya-outfit-uunp-hdt-need-this]Diablio link[/url]

CREDITS:
gutris1 for porting it to Skyrim
Diablio for UUNP version
